We're ready.

00:13.904 --> 00:16.447
I appreciate
your dedication, Alex.

00:16.657 --> 00:17.475
Don't do this! Joe!

00:17.557 --> 00:18.419
Something happened with Claire,

00:18.502 --> 00:19.300
