to witness her death.

00:23.512 --> 00:25.792
Will you grieve for your
love when she dies?

00:27.566 --> 00:28.150
Aah!

00:28.228 --> 00:29.230
Why does Claire have to die?

00:29.316 --> 00:31.954
It's so that you can be reborn.

00:34.159 --> 00:35.513
Unh!

00:38.193 --> 00:40.370
Joe, this is such a bad idea.

00:40.458 --> 00:41.205
Come on!

00:41.289 --> 00:44.147
Joe! Joe! Aah!

00:46.512 --> 00:47.678
Guys, we got a problem.

00:47.768 --> 00:48.726
Parker's missing.

00:48.816 --> 00:50.071
Any last words, Agent.

00:50.137 --> 00:50.990
You don't have to do this.

00:51.074 --> 00:51.969
Take small breaths.

00:52.060 --> 00:54.287
No! Somebody, help!

00:54.728 --> 00:57.486
Somebody!
Please. Aah!

01:00.435 --> 01:02.121
